{
  "chapter": 368,
  "chapter_summary": "第368章\"洛阳首富\"分两条线展开。寇仲化名\"莫一心\"随沙家船队入关，沙成功二少爷向他吹嘘沙家背景——洛阳首富，与独孤阀联姻，妹夫常何把守玄武门，此行受太子李建成庇护。沙成功请寇仲为红颜知己治病，竟是天下第一名妓尚秀芳，寇仲大惊。另一线，徐子陵化名\"莫为\"随关中剑派肖修明、谢家荣过桥，遭长林军尔文焕、乔公山、\"剑郎君\"卫家青拦路挑衅。徐子陵以一敌众，连挫尔文焕和卫家青，尚书封德彝路过喝止，公正处置责退长林军，并对徐子陵示好。次日寇仲在船上发现东溟号尾随，心虚躲回舱内。徐子陵与兴昌隆田三堂交谈，得知段爷调来关中剑派高手以抗长林军。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我当莫兄是自己人，才对你实说，今次我们是从洛阳溜出来的，王世充气运已尽，只看何日大唐精锐南来，把他收拾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "你们今趟到长安去，是否把落脚的地点安排妥当？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不瞒莫兄，我们沙家不单是洛阳的首富，家族中更不乏人累世为官。莫兄听过独孤阀吗？阀主独孤峰就是我爹的表弟。现在独孤阀得唐帝李渊照拂重用。我的四妹夫常何，不但是武林中有名的高手，更是御内猛将，负责把守长安宫城重地玄武门。我们今次到长安去，是得到建成太子的邀请庇护。过程惊险处，说出来你也不会相信。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "我今次是路遇贵人，原来二公子家世如此显赫。啊！施针确比用药更费精神。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "抵长安后，小弟尚有一事相求，请莫……兄万勿推却。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "我和二公子一见投缘，已成莫逆，二公子有甚么事可放心说出来，只要我莫嘿！只要鄙人力所能及，必为二公子办妥。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只是小事一件，小弟有位红颜知已，刻下正在长安。她也患有头痛症，不时发作。莫兄若能巧施回春妙手，小弟会非常感激。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "这么举手之劳的一件小事，有甚么问题？哈！二公子真风流。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这位美人儿堪称人间绝色，男人见到莫不动心。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "能令二公子梦萦魂牵的女子，究竟是何家小姐？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "她就是色艺双绝，名播大江南北，被誉为天下第一名妓的尚秀芳。",
      "tone": "悠然神往",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "莫兄见过她吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "text": "那轮得到我这种粗鄙低下的人去见她，鄙人只因能为她治病，感到莫大的荣幸吧！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_cheng_gong",
      "speaker_name": "沙成功",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当莫兄成为长安第一名医时，就再非低三下四的人。坦白说，开始时小弟一点都看不起莫兄，但现在莫兄却是我最尊敬的好朋友。只要有真材实学，再加点机缘，自有出头的一天。晚哩！成功再不敢阻莫兄休息。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "肖修明",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "尔文焕左边的是长林军校尉乔公山，右边那人是陇西派掌门金大桩座下三大弟子之一的'剑郎君'卫家青，三人均是长安有名的高手，莫兄小心。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_jia_rong",
      "speaker_name": "谢家荣",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们绝不可示弱，否则对方会得寸进尺，以后的日子更难过。无论甚么事，只要道理在我方，秦王府可为我们出头作主。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_wen_huan",
      "speaker_name": "尔文焕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "text": "原来是关中剑派的肖兄和谢兄，不见这么久，尔某还以为你们封剑归隐，听说兴昌隆近年大赚特赚，两位自然油水丰厚，可否借两个子儿让我们一众兄弟好到平康里快活快活。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_gong_shan",
      "speaker_name": "乔公山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "text": "如非尔将军提起关中剑派，我差点忘记，邱文盛自卜廷后就没收过弟子，是否改行跟徒弟卖盐呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_jia_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卫家青",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "text": "肖兄谢兄莫要怪尔兄和乔兄直肠直肚，有那句就说那句，皆因贵派这两年只懂逢迎秦王府，又偏袒好商，早惹起公愤。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "肖修明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卫兄这番话是甚么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长林军喽啰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "text": "卫爷说得这么清楚，你仍不明白吗？待老子解说你听，关中剑派的人都是马屁虫。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "借光！借光！老子没时间听你们的狂言乱语。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_wen_huan",
      "speaker_name": "尔文焕",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你是甚么人！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "text": "谢兄肖兄请为我押阵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_wen_huan",
      "speaker_name": "尔文焕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们宰了他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "speaker_name": "封德彝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_er_wen_huan",
      "speaker_name": "尔文焕",
      "listener": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "text": "卑职拜见封大人。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_gong_shan",
      "speaker_name": "乔公山",
      "listener": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "text": "此人摆明是来京城捣乱闹事，请封大人为我们主持公道，正之以法。",
      "tone": "愤慨",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "speaker_name": "封德彝",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这位仁兄高姓大名，是何方人士。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "text": "小民莫为，来自巴蜀，年来一直为兴昌隆办事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "speaker_name": "封德彝",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你的剑法非常出色，理该是大大有名的人，为何本官却从未听过你的大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "text": "小民的剑术传自家父莫一心，这两年才出来江湖行走，大人明察。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "speaker_name": "封德彝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事是非曲直，本官全看在眼内，你们拦道挑衅的恶霸行径，确是可恶，若非看在建成太子的脸上，今晚会教你们好看。还不给我滚！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_de_yi",
      "speaker_name": "封德彝",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "莫兄弟虽剑术高明，但长林军内高手如云，这几天最好暂避风头。再见！",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "text": "这人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "肖修明",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "莫兄确是鸿福当头，这人就是皇上的亲信大臣尚书省封德彝，连建成太子也要给足他面子。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "莫先生要到外面去吗？",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_fu",
      "text": "有甚么不安？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "自昨晚午夜起，有艘五桅大船从后追来，现在距我们不足半里，陈老师、毛老师等都在上面戒备。",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_fu",
      "text": "我叫甚么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你叫甚么名字？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_fu",
      "text": "此事说来好笑，家叔一向嫌我的本名莫大牛不好听，所以另外又改名作莫大，旋又觉这名字太妄自尊大，要另立新名，如此反覆改名换名，到现在搅得连我自己都弄不清楚该唤作甚么，只好下个决心，就拿家叔那天告知三少夫人的莫甚么作为名字算了。不知那天家叔用那个名字为三少夫人介绍小弟呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那莫先生就应是叫莫一心哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_sha_fu",
      "text": "哈！莫一心。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "text": "它可能亦是像我们般要入关中的船吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_shi_chang",
      "speaker_name": "毛世昌",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这艘是海船，吃水极深，如无必要，当不会学我们般连夜赶程，照我看事有可疑。",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_mao_shi_chang",
      "text": "此船正在加速，可在半个时辰内赶上我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_mao_shi_chang",
      "text": "这艘船不该是冲着我们来的。否则船上的投石机早装石待发了。嘿！我也该回去为老爷治病啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_san_tang",
      "speaker_name": "田三堂",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "有莫老师相助，是我们兴昌隆的福气。昨晚莫老师大发神威，狠挫尔文焕和乔公山等长林恶徒，不但为我们大大出一口恶气，还引起封大人的注意，实是一件好事。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tian_san_tang",
      "text": "我却正怕为田爷惹来麻烦呢。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_san_tang",
      "speaker_name": "田三堂",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "正如杜公所言，麻烦要来，避都避不了。段爷更声言寸步不能退让，兵来将挡，水来土掩。一切自有秦王担持。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 368,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
